"About Me" title is the same size and weight as every other section title — no hierarchy variation across the page. Fix: Vary size, weight, or spacing between section titles to create a sense of hierarchy rather than identical blocks stacked on each other.

"My Journey" subheading creates an awkward section-within-section. Fix: Remove it and fold the journey content directly under the About intro as a continuous paragraph.

Left text block is a dense wall of text with no visual breaks. Fix: Break into 2–3 shorter paragraphs with clear spacing between them.

Profile card floats too high relative to the text beside it. Fix: Use CSS flexbox align-items flex-start consistently so both columns start from the same baseline.

Left text and right card don't share a common vertical midpoint or baseline. Fix: Align both columns to a shared top axis, not floating independently.

