**SKILLS SECTION**

Six completely identical flat cards — no visual differentiation whatsoever. Fix: Replace with a grouped tag list, horizontal chip row, or a two-column categorized list instead of cards.

Card heights vary due to text length — breaks grid consistency. Fix: Use CSS Grid with align-items stretch so all cards in a row match height, or switch to a non-card layout entirely.

Icons are too small to read clearly. Fix: Increase icon size to at least 24–28px, or remove icons entirely if they add no real value.

Skill category names and tech listed below them have barely any size contrast. Fix: Make the category name at least 4–6px larger than the tech list text and use font-weight 600 on the heading.

