Tech tag badges are extremely small and hard to read. Fix: Increase font size to at least 11–12px, add more padding of 4px 10px, and give them a visible background.

"View Demo" and "View on GitHub" links inside cards are too small and cramped together. Fix: Increase link font size and add at least 8px gap between them.

Project descriptions are too long for cards — text gets cut off unevenly. Fix: Limit to 2 lines max using overflow hidden with webkit-line-clamp 2.

"View All Projects on GitHub" floats alone in empty space below the grid with no visual anchor. Fix: Style it as a subtle outlined button with proper margin-top 40px, centered — not a plain text link floating in space.

