Left contact info column and right form column have no visual divider or alignment relationship — just float beside each other. Fix: Add a vertical divider line between columns, or align both to a shared grid baseline so they feel structurally related.

"Let's Connect" block spacing from contact details above it is inconsistent. Fix: Add consistent margin-top of 32px between each contact info item and the Let's Connect block.

Social icons in contact section have no labels. Fix: Add text labels below or beside each icon.

