**FOOTER**

Footer is visually cramped — copyright text and social icons sit too close together. Fix: Add padding 24px top and bottom and use flexbox with justify-content space-between.

Social icons in footer are a third repeat of the same icons already shown in hero and contact. Fix: Remove footer social icons entirely — they have already appeared twice.

No visual separation between contact section and footer — they bleed into each other. Fix: Add a subtle 1px divider line or use a slightly different background opacity to create a clean boundary.

Copyright text and icons sit at the same visual weight with no hierarchy. Fix: Make copyright text smaller at around 13px with muted opacity so it clearly reads as secondary information.

